    • Transaction

      public Transaction(String transactionId, String email, int phoneNo, String name, int movieId, int cineplexId, int cinemaID, ArrayList<Integer> seatID, Date timing, double price)
      Parameters:
      transactionId - Unique Transaction ID based on requirement
      email - Email of User who book the ticket
      phoneNo - Phone no of User who book the ticket
      name - Movie Name
      movieId - Movie ID
      cineplexId - Cineplex ID of cineplex
      cinemaID - Hall of Cineplex
      seatID - Seat booked
      timing - Timing of movie
      price - Total price paid by user Constructor for a transaction object to be inserted into database
